Rating: 4
I was skeptical about the length of time to roast these but it's correct. I followed the recipe exactly except I did reduce the amount of oil. It was fantastic! I'll be making these again and again. I may try adding fresh herbs, garlic, or maybe mint just before serving. Endless possibilities, but good just as written. Was also great at room temp and would be excellent on brushcetta.

